commit.title: [ci] [appveyor] Move Appveyor to OPAM 2.
commit.message:
[ci] [appveyor] Move Appveyor to OPAM 2.

We update the Appveyor configuration so it uses OPAM 2.0, and thus it
can install newer packages.
